\n\n{{familytree|||!||||||!|||!||||!|}}\n{{familytree||A1|||||!||A2||A3|A1=<small>Victoria<br />b. 1862<br />m. Plyant Mahon</small>|A2=<small><span style=\"color:red;\">Ellison Mounts</span></small><span style=\"color:green;\">[12]</span>|A3=<small>Dr. [[Henry D. Hatfield|Henry D.]]<br />b. 1875<br />m. [[South Carolina \"Carrie\" Bronson Hatfield|South Carolina Bronson]]</small>}}\n{{familytree|||||||||!|}}\n{{familytree| |,|-|-|v|-|-|v|^|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|v|-|-|-|.| }}\n{{familytree|A1|A2|A3|A4|A5|A6|A7|A8|A9|A10|A11|A12|A13|\nA1=<small>Johnson<br />(Johnse)<br />b. 1862<br />m. Nancy <span style=\"color:orange;\">'''McCoy'''</span><br />m. Rebecca Browning<br />m. Roxie Browning<br />m. Nettie Toler</small>|\nA2=<small>William Anderson<br />(Cap)<br />b. 1864<br />m. Nancy Glenn</small>|\nA3=<small>Robert E. Lee<br />b. 1867<br />m. Mariah Wolford</small>|\nA4=<small>Nancy<br />b. 1869<br />m. John Vance<br />m. Charlie Mullens</small>|\nA5=<small>Elliott Rutherford<br />b. 1872<br />m. Margaret Shindler</small>|\nA6=<small>Mary<br />b. 1873<br />m. Frank Howes</small>|\nA7=<small>Elizabeth<br />b. 1875<br />m. John Caldwell</small>|\nA8=<small>Elias<br />b. 1878<br />m. Peggy Simple</small>|\nA9=<small>Detroit<br />(Troy)<br />b. 1881<br />m. Pearl</small>|\nA10=<small>Joseph<br />b. 1883<br />m. Grace Ferrell</small>|\nA11=<small>Rosada<br />b. 1885<br />m. Marion Browning</small>|\nA12=<small>Willis Wilson<br />b. 1888<br />m. Lakie Maynor<br />m. Ida Chafin</small>|\nA13=<small>Tennyson<br />(Tennis)<br />b. 1890<br />m. Lettie Hunter<br />m. Sadie Walters<br />m. Margaret</small>\n}}\n{{familytree/end}}\n{{hidden end}}\n\n==McCoy genealogy==\n\n===Randolph McCoy family tree===\nNames in <span style=\"color:red;\">red</span> indicate those who were killed as a direct result of the feud.<br />Names in <span style=\"color:orange;\">orange</span> highlight intermarriages between Hatfield and McCoy.<br />Numbers in <span style=\"c