{"title_page": "Titiwangsa Lake Gardens", "text_new": "{{Infobox park\n| name = Titiwangsa Lake Gardens\n| alt_name         = \n| native_name      = Taman Tasik Titiwangsa\n| native_name_lang = ms\n| image = Lake Titiwangsa.jpg\n| type = [[Urban park]]\n| location = [[Kuala Lumpur]], [[Federal Territory (Malaysia)|Federal Terrirory]]\n| area = {{Convert|95|ha|acre}}\n| created =\n| operator = [[Kuala Lumpur City Hall]]\n| visitation_num =\n| status = Open all year\n}}\n\n'''Titiwangsa Lake Gardens''' ({{lang-ms|Taman Tasik Titiwangsa}}) is a lake garden in [[Titiwangsa]], [[Kuala Lumpur]], [[Malaysia]].\n\n\u5176\u5b9e\u5c31\u4f4d\u4e8e\u5409\u9686\u5761\u5854\u9644\u8fd1\uff0c\u662f\u5409\u9686\u5761\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u539f\u59cb\u70ed\u5e26\u96e8\u6797\u3002\u5f53\u4f60\u8fdb\u5165\u516c\u56ed\uff0c\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u5173\u4e8e\u5404\u79cd\u751f\u6001\u751f\u6d3b\u7684\u5c55\u89c8\u3002\u5728\u8fd9\u5ea7\u68ee\u6797\u91cc\u6709\u4e00\u68f5\u903e\u767e\u5e74\u7684\u65e5\u843d\u6d1e\u6811\u3002\u6e38\u5ba2\u8fd8\u53ef\u8d70\u572870\u7c73\u9ad8\u7684\u540a\u6865\uff0c\u8ba9\u4f60\u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1\u6e38\u8d4f\u539f\u59cb\u68ee\u6797\u3002\u68ee\u6797\u5c40\u4e3a\u5343\u591a\u79cd\u690d\u7269\u8d34\u4e0a\u89e3\u8bf4\u6807\u7b7e\uff0c\u5305\u62ec\u70ed\u5e26\u96e8\u6797\u91cc\u7684\u7a00\u6709\u6811\u6728\u4e36\u7f55\u89c1\u836f\u8349\u4e36\u6500\u85e4\u4e0e\u8568\u7c7b\u690d\u7269\u4e36\u7ea2\u6728\u4e36\u9f99\u8111\u9999\u7b49\u3002\u5982\u679c\u90a3\u5929\u4f60\u5e78\u8fd0\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u8fd8\u53ef\u4ee5\u89c1\u5230\u5496\u5561\u5c71\u7684\u4e24\u79cd\u7334\u5b50\uff0c\u5373\u94f6\u53f6\u7334\u548c\u98df\u87f9\u7334\u3002\u5176\u4ed6\u8bbe\u65bd\u8fd8\u5305\u62ec\u89c2\u9e1f\u533a\u4e36\u9732\u8425\u6d3b\u52a8\u8349\u573a\u4e36\u77ad\u671b\u53f0\u4e36\u6162\u8dd1\u9053\u4ee5\u53ca\u4f11\u61a9\u51c9\u4ead\u7b49\u3002\u68ee\u6797\u5c40\u4e0d\u65f6\u4f1a\u4e3e\u529e\u6d3b\u52a8\uff0c\u5305\u62ec\u68ee\u6797\u6f2b\u6b65\u53ca\u591c\u95f4\u5f92\u6b65\u7a7f\u8d8a\u3002\n\n\u96ea\u5170\u83aa\u548c\u5409\u9686\u5761\u5e02\u533a\u7684\u4e00\u5ea7\u751f\u6001\u68ee\u6797\uff0c\u4e5f\u7b97\u662f\u5df4\u751f\u6cb3\u6d41\u57df\u7684\u7eff\u8272\u5fc3\u80ba\u3002\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u6709\u5f88\u591a\u5c71\u53ef\u4ee5\u8ba9\u4f60\u722c\u4e00\u722c\u3002\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u53ef\u4ee5\u8ba9\u4f60\u63a2\u9669\u7684\u5de8\u5927\u533a\u57df\u3002\u8fd9\u91cc\u8bbe\u6709\u6307\u6807\u666f\u70b9\uff0c\u6bd4\u5982\u77ad\u671b\u697c\u3001\u540a\u6865\u3001\u5c0f\u6eaa\u3001\u7535\u4fe1\u5854\u8fd8\u6709\u5370\u5ea6\u5e99\u3002\u52a0\u661f\u5c71\u6709\u4e24\u5ea7\u540a\u6865\uff0c\u5373\u539f\u59cb\u7ef3\u7d22\u540a\u6865\u4ee5\u53ca\u73b0\u4ee3\u94a2\u9aa8\u540a\u6865\u3002\u539f\u59cb\u7ef3\u7d22\u540a\u6865\u53ef\u4ee5\u901a\u5f80\u5c71\u5934\uff0c\u800c\u94a2\u9aa8\u540a\u6865\u8fd9\u8fb9\u6bd4\u8f83\u5148\u8fdb\uff0c\u8bbe\u6709\u53ef\u4ee5\u91ce\u9910\u7684\u5730\u65b9\u3002\u60f3\u8981\u6d41\u6c57\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u53c8\u4e0d\u60f3\u8d70\u5f97\u592a\u8f9b\u82e6\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u4e0d\u59a8\u6765\u8fd9\u91cc\u770b\u770b\uff0c\u53ef\u80fd\u8fd8\u4f1a\u9047\u5230\u7334\u5b50\u548c\u4f60\u4e00\u8d77\u540c\u884c\u3002\n\n==Facilities==\nThe lake garden has facilities such as jogging track, cycling track, kayaking, horse riding facility, radio control car racing track etc.<ref name=\"attractionsinmalaysia.com\">{{cite web|url=http://kuala-lumpur.attractionsinmalaysia.com/Titwangsa-Lake-Gardens.php|title=Titiwangsa Lake Garden (Taman Tasik Titiwangsa)|publisher=Attractions in Malaysia|accessdate=1 November 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Transport==\nThe lake garden is accessible within walking distance north east of [[Titiwangsa Station]].<ref name=\"attractionsinmalaysia.com\"/>\n\n==Opening time==\nThe park is opened everyday from 7:00 a.m. to 9:00 p.m. free of charge.<ref name=\"malaysia-traveller.com\"/>\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of tourist attractions in Kuala Lumpur]]\n* [[Mining in Malaysia]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.visitselangor.com/titiwangsa-park/ Titiwangsa Park] Lake gardens activities pricing and other information\n\n{{commons category|Titiwangsa Lake Gardens}}\n\n{{Coord|3|10|41.1|N|101|42|27.7|E|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Gardens in Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Geography of Kuala Lumpur]]\n[[Category:Lakes of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Kuala Lumpur]]\n\n{{Malaysia-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox park\n| name = Titiwangsa Lake Gardens\n| alt_name         = \n| native_name      = Taman Tasik Titiwangsa\n| native_name_lang = ms\n| image = Lake Titiwangsa.jpg\n| type = [[Urban park]]\n| location = [[Kuala Lumpur]], [[Federal Territory (Malaysia)|Federal Terrirory]]\n| area = {{Convert|95|ha|acre}}\n| created =\n| operator = [[Kuala Lumpur City Hall]]\n| visitation_num =\n| status = Open all year\n}}\n\n'''Titiwangsa Lake Gardens''' ({{lang-ms|Taman Tasik Titiwangsa}}) is a lake garden in [[Titiwangsa]], [[Kuala Lumpur]], [[Malaysia]].\n\n==History==\nThe gardens feature a huge central [[lake]] that was a byproduct of tin mining activities under [[British Malaya|British Rule]]. Later on, the area was cleaned up and developed into a park.<ref name=\"malaysia-traveller.com\">{{cite web|url=http://www.malaysia-traveller.com/titiwangsa-lake-gardens.html|title=Titiwangsa Lake Gardens|publisher=Malaysia Traveller|accessdate=1 November 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Geology==\nThe park spreads across an area of 95 hectares with a 57 hectares of lake.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.visitkl.gov.my/visitklv2/index.php?r=column/cthree&id=61&place_id=907|title=Titiwangsa Park|website=Visit KL|publisher=Tourism Unit, Kuala Lumpur City Hall|accessdate=1 November 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Facilities==\nThe lake garden has facilities such as jogging track, cycling track, kayaking, horse riding facility, radio control car racing track etc.<ref name=\"attractionsinmalaysia.com\">{{cite web|url=http://kuala-lumpur.attractionsinmalaysia.com/Titwangsa-Lake-Gardens.php|title=Titiwangsa Lake Garden (Taman Tasik Titiwangsa)|publisher=Attractions in Malaysia|accessdate=1 November 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Transport==\nThe lake garden is accessible within walking distance north east of [[Titiwangsa Station]].<ref name=\"attractionsinmalaysia.com\"/>\n\n==Opening time==\nThe park is opened everyday from 7:00 a.m. to 9:00 p.m. free of charge.<ref name=\"malaysia-traveller.com\"/>\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of tourist attractions in Kuala Lumpur]]\n* [[Mining in Malaysia]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.visitselangor.com/titiwangsa-park/ Titiwangsa Park] Lake gardens activities pricing and other information\n\n{{commons category|Titiwangsa Lake Gardens}}\n\n{{Coord|3|10|41.1|N|101|42|27.7|E|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Gardens in Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Geography of Kuala Lumpur]]\n[[Category:Lakes of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Kuala Lumpur]]\n\n{{Malaysia-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "14.192.212.49", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eGeology)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Titiwangsa_Lake_Gardens"}
